data.text:
TRS Turquesa Hotel is an adults-only hotel inside a resort. In the same resort, there are three family-friendly hotels which also belong to Palladium Hotel Group:

- Grand Palladium Punta Cana Resort & Spa

- Grand Palladium B√°varo Resort & Spa

- Grand Palladium Palace Resort Spa & Casino

As a guest of TRS Turquesa Hotel, you have full access to the facilities across all four hotels: pools, restaurants, bars, and more. This is a benefit that is exclusive to TRS guests; Grand Palladium guests cannot access the facilities at TRS Turquesa Hotel.

Golf carts routinely circulate the resort to facilitate transportation. However, the resort is highly walkable as well.
